# Copado Conflict Resolution - Files to exclude from automerge

# Profiles (often cause conflicts)
**/profiles/*.profile-meta.xml

# Permission Sets (manual review recommended)
**/permissionsets/*.permissionset-meta.xml

# System Administrator metadata
**/profiles/Admin.profile-meta.xml
**/profiles/System Administrator.profile-meta.xml

# Package.xml (always review manually)
manifest/package.xml

# Org-specific settings
**/settings/*.settings-meta.xml

# Large static resources (binary conflicts)
**/staticresources/*.resource

# Custom Metadata with environment-specific values
# **/customMetadata/*.md-meta.xml

# Translations (if managed separately)
# **/objectTranslations/*.objectTranslation-meta.xml
# **/translations/*.translation-meta.xml
